<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><xfdf xmlns="http://ns.adobe.com/xfdf/" xml:space="preserve"><fields/><annots><highlight page="8" rect="143.280,541.662,464.520,597.519" color="#FFCD45" flags="print" name="2790deb6-b892-e41b-d4e8-8d316c220d7f" title="Guest" subject="高亮" date="D:20220209165930+08'00'" creationdate="D:20220209165930+08'00'" coords="333.18000000000006,597.518525,445.12800000000004,597.518525,333.18000000000006,584.862275,445.12800000000004,584.862275,143.28,583.118525,464.52,583.118525,143.28,570.481025,464.52,570.481025,143.28,568.718525,461.568,568.718525,143.28,556.062275,461.568,556.062275,143.28,554.318525,344.028,554.318525,143.28,541.662275,344.028,541.662275"><contents>Between his memory
and its reflection there is a wall and it cannot be pierced. The
past belongs to the past and the survivor does not recognize
himself in the words linking him to it.</contents></highlight><highlight page="8" rect="143.280,484.062,460.884,539.919" color="#FFCD45" flags="print" name="2be01790-f69c-ac67-863a-53cad54e1ce3" title="Guest" subject="高亮" date="D:20220209170007+08'00'" creationdate="D:20220209170007+08'00'" coords="179.28,539.918525,460.884,539.918525,179.28,527.262275,460.884,527.262275,143.28,525.518525,451.284,525.518525,143.28,512.881025,451.284,512.881025,143.28,511.118525,457.55999999999995,511.118525,143.28,498.462275,457.55999999999995,498.462275,143.28,496.718525,197.55599999999998,496.718525,143.28,484.062275,197.55599999999998,484.062275"><contents>“The survivors of the Holocaust who tell their stories
bear witness, transmit a spark of the flame, tell a fragment
of the tale and remember for those who begged them to tell
the story.”</contents></highlight><highlight page="8" rect="143.280,311.262,456.432,381.519" color="#FFCD45" flags="print" name="0dea2129-3dc8-6cc3-1ab0-944909d76fef" title="Guest" subject="高亮" date="D:20220209170100+08'00'" creationdate="D:20220209170100+08'00'" coords="179.28,381.51852500000007,452.84399999999994,381.51852500000007,179.28,368.86227500000007,452.84399999999994,368.86227500000007,143.28,367.1185250000001,456.432,367.1185250000001,143.28,354.4622750000001,456.432,354.4622750000001,143.28,352.7185250000001,435.15599999999995,352.7185250000001,143.28,340.0622750000001,435.15599999999995,340.0622750000001,143.28,338.3185250000001,451.764,338.3185250000001,143.28,325.6622750000001,451.764,325.6622750000001,143.28,323.9185250000001,344.784,323.9185250000001,143.28,311.2622750000001,344.784,311.2622750000001"><contents>There is an irony in the stories of Sonia and of other
survivors of the Holocaust, which puzzles me deeply. How
out of such darkness shines their light, out of such hate
comes their love, out of such degradation shows their dig-
nity, out of such despair is their hope?</contents></highlight><highlight page="8" rect="143.280,253.662,467.592,309.519" color="#FFCD45" flags="print" name="5822f7f3-862a-5448-619a-98105c36463d" title="Guest" subject="高亮" date="D:20220209170124+08'00'" creationdate="D:20220209170124+08'00'" coords="179.28,309.5185250000001,452.41200000000015,309.5185250000001,179.28,296.8622750000001,452.41200000000015,296.8622750000001,143.28,295.1185250000001,452.172,295.1185250000001,143.28,282.4622750000001,452.172,282.4622750000001,143.28,280.7185250000001,439.9200000000001,280.7185250000001,143.28,268.0622750000001,439.9200000000001,268.0622750000001,143.28,266.31852500000014,467.592,266.31852500000014,143.28,253.66227500000014,467.592,253.66227500000014"><contents>Sonia is a teacher. She believes that the students and
adults she reaches can take a leap into her past and emerge
with the courage to care more about their neighbors. She
brings new meaning to the saying, “a teacher affects eternity.”</contents></highlight><highlight page="9" rect="143.280,103.805,467.760,181.564" color="#FFCD45" flags="print" name="57e779e6-54d4-85bc-6f27-c1e144c43fd6" title="Guest" subject="高亮" date="D:20220209200532+08'00'" creationdate="D:20220209200532+08'00'" coords="179.28,181.5640249999999,457.092,181.5640249999999,179.28,168.9077749999999,457.092,168.9077749999999,143.28,167.1640249999998,467.76,167.1640249999998,143.28,154.5077749999998,467.76,154.5077749999998,299.664,115.85202499999991,312.33187499999997,115.85202499999991,299.664,103.80514999999991,312.33187499999997,103.80514999999991"><contents>Genocide is the end result of hatred, prejudice, igno-
rance, and indifference. When scapegoating and stereotyping
IX
go unchallenged, sooner or later we all become enslaved.
Those of us who survived that other universe where the
darkness was almost complete have an obligation to warn
you, because we know that under the right conditions it can
happen again, anywhere, to any people.</contents></highlight><highlight page="10" rect="143.280,445.799,464.052,544.855" color="#FFCD45" flags="print" name="c7e8481e-4613-cf06-058b-7647c9589a91" title="Guest" subject="高亮" date="D:20220209201138+08'00'" creationdate="D:20220209201138+08'00'" coords="179.28,544.8551249999999,440.0640000000001,544.8551249999999,179.28,532.1988749999999,440.0640000000001,532.1988749999999,143.28,530.455125,450.44399999999996,530.455125,143.28,517.798875,450.44399999999996,517.798875,143.28,516.055125,464.052,516.055125,143.28,503.398875,464.052,503.398875,143.28,501.655125,439.65599999999995,501.655125,143.28,488.998875,439.65599999999995,488.998875,143.28,487.255125,447.592265625,487.255125,143.28,474.598875,447.592265625,474.598875,143.28,472.855125,451.87199999999996,472.855125,143.28,460.198875,451.87199999999996,460.198875,143.28,458.455125,313.86,458.455125,143.28,445.798875,313.86,445.798875"><contents>Normal standards do not apply to the Holocaust.
Even language fails and words like hunger, fear, hot, cold,
and pain lose their meaning. In fact, the Holocaust is a crime
without a language. Yet we must speak about it, and we
must remember from generation to generation, because if
we remember, then memory will (we hope) shield us from
repeating such unthinkable evil.</contents></highlight><highlight page="10" rect="143.280,172.199,399.048,372.055" color="#FFCD45" flags="print" name="eae9ffef-495f-d77b-66dd-3367fe5abb1f" title="Guest" subject="高亮" date="D:20220209202646+08'00'" creationdate="D:20220209202646+08'00'" coords="143.28,372.055125,236.50799999999998,372.055125,143.28,359.398875,236.50799999999998,359.398875,143.28,343.255125,327.744,343.255125,143.28,330.598875,327.744,330.598875,143.28,328.85512500000004,349.284,328.85512500000004,143.28,316.19887500000004,349.284,316.19887500000004,143.28,314.45512500000007,360.576,314.45512500000007,143.28,301.79887500000007,360.576,301.79887500000007,143.28,300.05512500000003,356.20799999999997,300.05512500000003,143.28,287.39887500000003,356.20799999999997,287.39887500000003,143.28,285.65512500000006,278.904,285.65512500000006,143.28,272.998875,278.904,272.998875,143.28,256.85512500000004,327.744,256.85512500000004,143.28,244.19887500000004,327.744,244.19887500000004,143.28,242.45512500000007,349.284,242.45512500000007,143.28,229.79887500000007,349.284,229.79887500000007,143.28,228.05512499999998,337.5,228.05512499999998,143.28,215.39887499999998,337.5,215.39887499999998,143.28,213.655125,399.048,213.655125,143.28,200.998875,399.048,200.998875,143.28,199.2551249999999,342.552,199.2551249999999,143.28,186.5988749999999,342.552,186.5988749999999,143.28,184.85512499999993,267.456,184.85512499999993,143.28,172.19887499999993,267.456,172.19887499999993"><contents>For Yom Ha ‘Shoah
Come, take this giant leap with me
into the other world . . . the other place
where language fails and imagery defies,
denies man’s consciousness . . . and dies
upon the altar of insanity.
Come, take this giant leap with me
into the other world . . . the other place
and trace the eclipse of humanity . . .
where children burned while mankind stood by,
and the universe has yet to learn why
. . .has yet to learn why.</contents></highlight><highlight page="11" rect="162,375.156,278.743,390.924" color="#FFCD45" flags="print" name="f6b831db-eb5a-d109-1e4c-399480bc89e3" title="Guest" subject="高亮" date="D:20220209202933+08'00'" creationdate="D:20220209202933+08'00'" coords="162,390.92409999999995,278.7432,390.92409999999995,162,375.1561,278.7432,375.1561"><contents>My home was in Poland</contents></highlight><highlight page="11" rect="144,361.176,477.883,390.924" color="#FFCD45" flags="print" name="1d07b914-0f1f-ab59-021c-52ec6e61bce6" title="Guest" subject="高亮" date="D:20220209202956+08'00'" creationdate="D:20220209202956+08'00'" coords="473.8872000000001,390.92409999999995,477.8832000000001,390.92409999999995,473.8872000000001,375.1561,477.8832000000001,375.1561,144,376.9441,467.5511999999999,376.9441,144,361.1761,467.5511999999999,361.1761"><contents>I
was born there in the beautiful old city of Kraków in August, 1928.</contents></highlight><highlight page="11" rect="144,319.236,467.401,348.984" color="#FFCD45" flags="print" name="9160b574-145f-c487-cd7a-ae1232775e37" title="Guest" subject="高亮" date="D:20220209203029+08'00'" creationdate="D:20220209203029+08'00'" coords="354.5148,348.9841,467.4012,348.9841,354.5148,333.21610000000004,467.4012,333.21610000000004,144,335.00410000000005,256.23839999999996,335.00410000000005,144,319.2361,256.23839999999996,319.2361"><contents>My mother’s name was
Adela Finder Schreiber</contents></highlight><highlight page="11" rect="144,263.316,493.555,293.064" color="#FFCD45" flags="print" name="b19fc3ab-4f8e-61b2-ed64-ae17b3865145" title="Guest" subject="高亮" date="D:20220209203838+08'00'" creationdate="D:20220209203838+08'00'" coords="162,293.06410000000005,493.55520000000024,293.06410000000005,162,277.2961,493.55520000000024,277.2961,144,279.08410000000003,454.20720000000006,279.08410000000003,144,263.3161,454.20720000000006,263.3161"><contents>My father, Janek Schreiber, was a middle-class businessman. He had
a small shop in Kraków where he sold leather and shoe supplies.</contents></highlight><highlight page="13" rect="144,381.396,489.732,425.124" color="#FFCD45" flags="print" name="2d1fbe6c-4bf6-07dc-ef5e-08f41c342856" title="Guest" subject="高亮" date="D:20220209204931+08'00'" creationdate="D:20220209204931+08'00'" coords="390.62640000000016,425.12400000000014,484.7640000000003,425.12400000000014,390.62640000000016,409.3560000000001,484.7640000000003,409.3560000000001,144,411.1440000000001,489.732,411.1440000000001,144,395.37600000000015,489.732,395.37600000000015,144,397.16400000000016,238.4352,397.16400000000016,144,381.39600000000013,238.4352,381.39600000000013"><contents>This was especially
true when Poland faced bad times. When the Polish people suffered, the
Jewish people bled.</contents></highlight><highlight page="19" rect="144,221.376,494.124,335.004" color="#FFCD45" flags="print" name="a0e32d8d-a780-9c57-58fd-37739774a2f2" title="Guest" subject="高亮" date="D:20220213222437+08'00'" creationdate="D:20220213222437+08'00'" coords="163.20000000000002,335.00410000000005,489.6540000000003,335.00410000000005,163.20000000000002,319.2361,489.6540000000003,319.2361,144,321.02410000000003,465.95280000000025,321.02410000000003,144,305.25610000000006,465.95280000000025,305.25610000000006,144,307.04410000000007,465.6696,307.04410000000007,144,291.27610000000004,465.6696,291.27610000000004,144,293.06410000000005,478.99439999999987,293.06410000000005,144,277.2961,478.99439999999987,277.2961,144,279.08410000000003,489.0912,279.08410000000003,144,263.3161,489.0912,263.3161,144,265.1041,483.05519999999996,265.1041,144,249.3361000000001,483.05519999999996,249.3361000000001,144,251.1241000000001,494.124,251.1241000000001,144,235.35610000000008,494.124,235.35610000000008,144,237.1441000000001,389.96039999999994,237.1441000000001,144,221.37610000000018,389.96039999999994,221.37610000000018"><contents>Uncle Henek was out of town when the Gestapo (the German secret
police) came for him. The Gestapo arrested my aunt instead. When
Henek learned of her arrest, he hurried back to save her. The Nazis
released Sonia, who rushed home to Vitek, their only son. (Both were
later killed in the Rzeszów Ghetto.) The Gestapo then sent Henek along
with other leaders of Rzeszów to the newly-built Auschwitz, which, in
1940, functioned as a camp for political prisoners. Some weeks later, my
Aunt Sonia received her husband’s ashes in an urn.</contents></highlight><highlight page="22" rect="144,619.056,461.686,648.804" color="#FFCD45" flags="print" name="6f9ffff4-94e0-6655-567c-4b1f820ede11" title="Guest" subject="高亮" date="D:20220213222546+08'00'" creationdate="D:20220213222546+08'00'" coords="244.34640000000002,648.804,461.6856000000001,648.804,244.34640000000002,633.0360000000001,461.6856000000001,633.0360000000001,144,634.8240000000001,447.90000000000003,634.8240000000001,144,619.056,447.90000000000003,619.056"><contents>Instead my mother, father, and I—along with
thousands of other Jews—were forced into the Kraków Ghetto.</contents></highlight></annots><pages><defmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,-90,715.6800000000001"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="1"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="2"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="3"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="4"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="5"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="6"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="7"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="8"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="9"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="10"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="11"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="12"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="13"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="14"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="15"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="16"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="17"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="18"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="19"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="20"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="21"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="22"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="23"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="24"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="25"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="26"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="27"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="28"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="29"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="30"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="31"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="32"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="33"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="34"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="35"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="36"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="37"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="38"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="39"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="40"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="41"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="42"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="43"/><pgmtx matrix="1,0,0,-1,0,792" page="44"/><pgmtx matrix=